OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FThe St. Petersburg International
OL,7,FEconomic Forum began in Russia on
OL,8,FFriday with a rejection from President
OL,9,FPutin to talk peace with Ukraine's
OL,10,FPresident Zelenskyy, as ITV News
OL,11,FCorrespondent John Ray reports.
OL,13,FRussian President Vladimir Putin on
OL,14,FFriday rejected a proposal by
OL,15,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,16,FZelenskyy for a face-to-face meeting
OL,17,Fon the four-year-old conflict, saying
OL,18,Fhe sees "no point" in meeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FThursday's letter, the first public
OL,7,Fmessage Zelenskyy has written directly
OL,8,Fto Putin since Russia sent troops into
OL,9,FUkraine in 2022, was a critique of the
OL,10,FRussian leader's 26 years in power and
OL,11,Fincluded some taunts about his age.
OL,13,FSpeaking at the St. Petersburg
OL,14,FInternational Economic Forum, Putin
OL,15,Fdescribed Zelenskyy's open letter
OL,16,Fproposing the meeting as "boorish."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,F"Is it a way to create conditions for
OL,7,Fpersonal meetings and talks, or create
OL,8,Fan environment which makes any
OL,9,Fpersonal meetings impossible?" Putin
OL,10,Fsaid at a question-and-answer session
OL,11,Fat his annual St. Petersburg
OL,12,FInternational Economic Forum. "I think
OL,13,Fit's the second", he added.
OL,15,FPutin said that a Russian businessman
OL,16,Fwhom he didn't identify travelled to
OL,17,FKyiv last month and met with Zelenskyy
OL,18,Fto hear his offer of a personal
OL,19,Fmeeting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FHowever, Putin said that he currently
OL,7,Fsees "no point" in such a meeting,
OL,8,Ffollowing a May 22 drone attack by
OL,9,FUkraine on a college dormitory in the
OL,10,FRussian-controlled Luhansk region that
OL,11,FMoscow said killed 21 and wounded
OL,12,Fscores of others.
OL,14,FIn response to Zelenskyy's barbs about
OL,15,Fhis age and long stay in power, the 73-
OL,16,Fyear-old Putin pointed at other global
OL,17,Fleaders who are older, adding that
OL,18,F"the main thing isn't age; the main
OL,19,Fthing is the ability to work."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FHe also mocked Zelenskyy's rocky Oval
OL,7,FOffice meeting in 2025 and thanked US
OL,8,FPresident Donald Trump for "educating"
OL,9,FZelenskyy "before the eyes of the
OL,10,Fwhole world" and teaching him a proper
OL,11,Fdress code.
OL,13,F"There is still a lot to be done," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FZelenskyy acknowledged shifting US
OL,7,Fpriorities, saying it would be wrong
OL,8,Fto simply wait for the Trump
OL,9,Fadministration to return its attention
OL,10,Fto ending the fighting in Ukraine
OL,11,Fwhile it remains heavily focused on
OL,12,Fthe Iran war.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FIn Washington, Trump said Thursday it
OL,20,F"would be great" if Putin and
OL,21,FZelenskyy met.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FPutin has previously offered for
OL,7,FZelenskyy to come to Moscow for talks,
OL,8,Fan offer that the Ukrainian leader
OL,9,Frejected.
OL,11,FPutin said last month he doesn't
OL,12,Fexclude a meeting in a third country,
OL,13,Fbut only when there is a deal to sign.
OL,15,FOn Thursday, Putin again rejected
OL,16,FZelenskyy's push for an immediate
OL,17,Fceasefire, arguing that Moscow wants a
OL,18,Fcomprehensive settlement, not a
OL,19,Ftemporary truce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FThe Russian president said Moscow is
OL,7,Fopen to a compromise on Ukraine in
OL,8,Fline with understandings reached at
OL,9,Flast year's summit with Trump in
OL,10,FAnchorage, Alaska, adding that Ukraine
OL,11,Fneeds to accept them to make a deal to
OL,12,Fend the conflict.
OL,14,F"Naturally, the Ukrainian side would
OL,15,Flike us to suspend the advances made
OL,16,Fby Russian troops," he said. "But it
OL,17,Fwould be better to end the war by
OL,18,Fagreeing to the compromises that were
OL,19,Fdiscussed in Anchorage."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
