PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,FAsked about Iran, Putin voiced hope
OL,7,Ffor an eventual deal to secure lasting
OL,8,Fpeace.
OL,10,FHe shrugged off claims that Moscow
OL,11,Fprovided Iran with satellite images,
OL,12,Fsaying that Tehran could use widely
OL,13,Favailable commercial ones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
