FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1780711406
OL,3,CPutin rejects Zelenskyy's offer to
OL,4,Cmeet saying there is 'no point' to it
OL,6,F"As for weapons, Iran hasn't asked us
OL,7,Ffor them and we haven't supplied any
OL,8,Fweapons to Iran," he said, adding that
OL,9,FRussia stands ready to take enriched
OL,10,Furanium for storage as part of a
OL,11,Fpotential peace deal, and that Moscow
OL,12,Fhas stayed in contact with Iran, the
OL,13,FUS and Israel.
